# Breaking changes #
> Added `magic.Color`
  > `.black`
  > `.red`
  > `.green`
  > `.yellow`
  > `.blue`
  > `.magenta`
  > `.cyan`
  > `.white`
  > `.reset`
> Added `magic.Style`
  > `.default`
  > `.bright`
  > `.underlined`
  > `.blinking`
  > `.fixed_color`
> Added `magic.Highlight`
  > '.black`
  > '.red`
  > '.green`
  > '.yellow`
  > '.blue`
  > '.magenta`
  > '.cyan`
  > '.white`
> Added `magic.Print`
  > '.text(...)'
  > '.type(...)'
> Added `magic.Get`
  > '.colored_text(...)'
  > '.layout(...)'

